These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the fan of funk is between the fan of reggae and the fan of trance##2
2. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | punk | trance | funk | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, milk, sprite
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | sprite | coffee | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, hedgehog, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | cat | snake | hedgehog | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
